    "description": "<strong> 《血腥恐怖植物》--可能是史上最血腥的点击式休闲冒险游戏！帮助 恐怖植物 解决有趣好玩的点击谜题，杀死邪恶的小矮人，拯救森林和森林里的生物！</strong><br>一片美丽、悠闲的森林里生活着快乐的生物，现在却被邪恶的矮人占领了。使用食肉恐怖植物探索邪恶矮人的居住地。查看森林布局，深入地下，爬上高树，将他们一网打尽，保护大自然。微妙的幽默和大量邪恶矮人的鲜血！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304590/extras/7445dd79d1548a84c8e414562658a3ed.poster.avif?t=1765749104\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304590/extras/7445dd79d1548a84c8e414562658a3ed.webm?t=1765749104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304590/extras/7445dd79d1548a84c8e414562658a3ed.mp4?t=1765749104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你能战胜邪恶的矮人，让森林重获和平吗？<br><br>■ 轻松而刺激的游戏玩法。通过与环境互动和解决小的点击/隐藏物品谜题，引导恐怖植物穿过独特的地点。容易上手，却难以放下。<br><br>■ 独特而奇特的手绘 2D 艺术风格和 2D 动画。<br><br>■ 通过身临其境的有趣角色配音、轻松愉悦的自然环境音效和引人入胜的故事情节，探索一个充满冒险的世界。<br><br>■ 少数关卡有多个结局，千万不要错过！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304590/extras/5fe1d4950c10461dddcbf3d13e79dd83.poster.avif?t=1765749104\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304590/extras/5fe1d4950c10461dddcbf3d13e79dd83.webm?t=1765749104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2304590/extras/5fe1d4950c10461dddcbf3d13e79dd83.mp4?t=1765749104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
